This is the TED-LIUM corpus release 1, 
licensed under Creative Commons BY-NC-ND 3.0 (http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/3.0/deed.en).

All talks and text are property of TED Conferences LLC.

---

Contents:

- 774 audio talks in NIST sphere format (SPH)
- 774 aligned automatic transcripts in STM format
- Dictionary with pronunciation (157617 words)

---

SPH Header info:

sample_n_bytes 2
channel_count 1
sample_byte_format 10
sample_rate 16000
sample_coding pcm

---

A. Rousseau, P. Deléglise, and Y. Estève, "TED-LIUM: an automatic speech recognition dedicated corpus",
in Proceedings of the Eighth International Conference on Language Resources and Evaluation (LREC’12), May 2012.
